name: R.O.B.O.T. Discovers His Powers
description: Growing up, I knew there was something different about me. People where I grew up were not interested in books, information, or knowledge. I was never physically strong, so I cultivated a powerful brain and a sharp wit as my defense. Over time, I became powerful enough to escape my old life, but I could not tell how toxic I had become to do it. In my ambition to escape, I became a supervillain.
